---
description: Checklist for privacy and security review of prompts, workflows, and data handling
alwaysApply: false
globs:
  - "**/*.py"
  - "**/*.js"
  - "**/*.ts"
  - "**/*.md"
  - "**/*.txt"
---

privacy-review-checklist:

- Confirm no unprotected PII is exposed in prompts or API calls.
- Verify sensitive data uses appropriate protection method (mask, redact, or tokenize).
- Check for hardcoded credentials or API keys; use environment variables instead.
- Validate that semantic guardrails are applied to multi-turn conversations.
- Ensure configuration specifies correct entity types for detection.
- Confirm protection policies align with data classification levels.
- Review audit logs for any failed protection operations.
- Document data lineage and transformation pipelines.
